item.title: Netbeans OS X Launcher : My First Open Source Project
item.description: After many many years of open source advocacy, I have finally created my own first open source project. I have really started small. Too small actually. Netbeans So whats this all about? This application is a simple launcher for Netbeans. I have no prior experience in Mac OS X application development. This is not even a full blown application, per say. Its just an Automator workflow.

item.title: How to use UOB Internet Banking on Chrome/Safari on MAC OS X Lion
item.description: I have been suffering with login issues on UOB internet banking site for as long as I can remember. I had to use Windows on a virtual machine to always login on UOB internet banking site.
